Source: block-copy-command
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/rustwizard/block_copy_command

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-block-copy-command
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-block-copy-command
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: COPY command firewall for PostgreSQL
 block_copy_command blocks COPY TO, COPY FROM, and COPY PROGRAM through a
 ProcessUtility hook that is loaded from shared_preload_libraries.
 It provides runtime GUCs for selective blocking and audit logging across
 PostgreSQL 14 through 18.
